short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Browser extension for interacting with Avvy Domains

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Avvy Domains is a naming service designed to support the Avalanche ecosystem and its various subnets.

Interact with .avax domains from your web browser.
